{
  "stem": "19211.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because somebody told him-- must have told him where we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he crawled down into the hole and he said, nobody is there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, you figure it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, I can't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So isn't that luck?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's pure luck.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There are other escapes that I had that were minor, smaller.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They caught us in the woods, some Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were walking in the woods, and they were walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were like, Ukrainian partisans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we-- as soon as we saw them, we ran.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew the woods pretty well too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't run after us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was another.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like, they had their weapons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't shoot after us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Close call again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And luck.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That there is nothing more that I can describe than it was lucky that we was-- that we survived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as a family, yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's unusual.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But one thing all the-- all the families-- I told you that before, I think-- survived that were in the bunkers with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All except the two people that got killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't because they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans were actually afraid or they didn't have enough equipment to come to the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they were losing the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they needed every tank and every soldier sent to the war, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were afraid for the partisans too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Partisans were shooting them-- at them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they're killing them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't have enough manpower to really send to the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe that was another luck-- lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they could have come and they could have found us right away, where we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't that difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were afraid, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
